Interface ArchitecturalElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Architecture, Component, ComponentType, Connector, Exception, Interface, InterfaceType, MethodSpecification, MonitoredProperty, Parameter, ParameterType, PerformanceStats, ProvidedInterface, RequiredInterface, Tenant
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArchitecturalElementImpl, ArchitectureImpl, ComponentImpl, ComponentTypeImpl, ConnectorImpl, ExceptionImpl, InterfaceImpl, InterfaceTypeImpl, MethodSpecificationImpl, MonitoredPropertyImpl, ParameterImpl, ParameterTypeImpl, PerformanceStatsImpl, ProvidedInterfaceImpl, RequiredInterfaceImpl, TenantImpl

    public interface ArchitecturalElement
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Architectural Element'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Uid
    • Criticality
    • Monitored Properties
    • Issue Impacts
    • Strategy Inputs
    • Working Data Elements
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getArchitecturalElement()
